p; Co Inc.\">SHCO</a></span>) recently announced its quarterly results which also included the company's confirmation of a buyout offer and this resulted in the company's share price to appreciate close to 50% in one day. While this wasn't</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/646653958/image_646653958.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745529-soho-house-could-go-private-again-only-3-years-after-ipo", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 16:30:45", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745551", "title": "How To Use Leverage To Boost Your Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rear view of young man walking towards detour\" data-id=\"1253985593\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8660px\" height=\"5773px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1